</ACTION>
<SUMMARY>
SUMMARY:

 On November 18, 1993 EPA's Office of Pollution Prevention and Toxics published a proposed rule to amend the requirements
that govern the reclassification of certain PCB and PCB-Contaminated Transformers to a lower regulatory status
as a PCB-Contaminated (

